<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-07-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-07-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="51" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d51">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111/3880</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Roumania</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_VCJ1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Vopicka</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucharest</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-07-22">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 22, 1916, noon</hi>
                                </date>.<lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received July 24, 10 p.
                                m.</hi>]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>279. Roumania has received from Russia 60 cars of ammunition and
                            prominent Roumanian general informs me will receive within 10 days 100
                            cars more. This seems positively to indicate an agreement between Russia
                            and Roumania. Will keep Department informed as to further
                            developments.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_VCJ1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Vopicka</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>